---
title: Smoked Ham & Cheese Subs with Romaine Wedge Salad and Creamy Italian Dressing
description: Whether you call them subs, hoagies, heroes, or grinders, these substantial sandwiches deliver on flavor! Smoked ham and mild Monterey Jack cheese are layered on a toasted baguette spread with creamy Italian dressing and topped with shredded lettuce and juicy tomato slices. A crisp wedge salad served alongside completes this quick and tasty dish.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/6627cc8c2fa454163f2118ae-35d836c7.jpeg
